{"type": "article", "id": 18613, "title": "这位纽约摄影师，将生活垃圾拍出了仪式感", "description": "在镜头下，这些日常生活中的垃圾呈现出了奇怪的庄严感——一种无聊的魅力。", "date": "2015-12-08T07:30:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7319, "name": "摄影师"}, {"id": 117, "name": "纽约"}, {"id": 7781, "name": "垃圾"}, {"id": 19910, "name": "David Brandon"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 145, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607124057Ne7b8vxI1htEoaMw.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t平日里，<a href=\"http://davidbrandongeeting.com\" target=\"_blank\">纽约摄影师 David Brandon </a>感到挺无聊的。无聊到一定程度，他就开始拍街上的垃圾——空漱口水瓶、废弃的纸巾盒、飘舞的塑料袋、被丢弃的键盘，这些被遗弃的生活用品是他的最爱。垃圾越拍越多，<a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/david-brandon-geeting-4\" target=\"_blank\">他就把这系列照片集合起来，搞了个展览</a>，名叫 Waste Management 。在展览照片中，他使用了大量拼贴效果，日常的垃圾呈现出了一种奇怪的庄严感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124043aekOY9GJhn635NbZ.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124043CK1JxFUHVO0uP54q.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124044jprC01hyWZ36KnPw.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124045hsGNVubPLBpvq1Hj.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"1.33263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124045U8pJwc4Lt052YzeS.jpg\" title=\"David Brandon Geeting: Waste Management\" alt=\"David Brandon Geeting: Waste Management\" data-ratio=\"1.33287293\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124046oXgxNTK3m1PElRFC.jpg\" title=\"David Brandon Geeting: Waste Management\" alt=\"David Brandon Geeting: Waste Management\" data-ratio=\"1.33287293\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124047KNDCkYW5phdRneO3.jpg\" title=\"David Brandon Geeting: Waste Management\" alt=\"David Brandon Geeting: Waste Management\" data-ratio=\"1.328\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span>David Brandon Geeting: Waste Management</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124047DNFurRtgyT1PS0W4.jpg\" title=\"展览现场\" alt=\"展览现场\" data-ratio=\"0.66421053\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><span style=\"text-align:center;\">Waste Management 展</span>览现场</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124048jTB4Z3PCsAuaS8wO.jpg\" title=\"展览现场\" alt=\"展览现场\" data-ratio=\"1.50631579\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><span style=\"text-align:center;\">展</span><span style=\"text-align:center;\"></span><span style=\"text-align:center;\">览现场</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t当然，David 的工作不仅是“拍垃圾”啦，他的本职工作是时尚摄影师。以下是他拍摄的时尚摄影作品，与景物摄影一样，<a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/david-brandon-geeting-2\" target=\"_blank\">时尚照片也带有鲜明的复古风格</a>，很特别。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124048K0efaHx8DWRcyMkB.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.50084034\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124049yGoQwesEUAhmjW2r.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.50084034\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124049A8yQxNLdlWEjY1Km.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.50084034\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t下图是 <span>David Brandon Geeting </span>出版的一本书，叫作 <span style=\"text-align:center;\">Infinite Power</span><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124050AS3f8TUiR6w1FYnx.jpg\" title=\"Infinite Power\" alt=\"Infinite Power\" data-ratio=\"0.66386555\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Infinite Power 摄影集</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124051EgV2GQZBIfM4c1is.jpg\" title=\"Infinite Power\" alt=\"Infinite Power\" data-ratio=\"0.66386555\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Infinite Power</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071240515stoTcAwRri3q1GS.jpg\" title=\"Infinite Power\" alt=\"Infinite Power\" data-ratio=\"0.66386555\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Infinite Power</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124051y58R2BLbU1O0fcTC.jpg\" title=\"其他摄影作品\" alt=\"其他摄影作品\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span><span style=\"text-align:center;\">David Brandon 的其</span>他摄影作品</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124052imkNElJB7QP86TMW.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124052Mg1pZNbDvU7B2nuj.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124053X2vtxTfu6GdLJ9K1.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071240538wmsJnC5fWE16XGt.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>David </span>善用闪光灯，对物品还有着特殊的空间感，这使得他的作品在千篇一律的摄影作品里显得很特别。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071240542ViQOP6a1GRcZJdX.gif\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.32380952\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124055YMTmE1KWZ3spP6SB.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.33368421\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124055qEZw6VFmWIAxkTCO.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.33263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124056r9uhHPXUB53y427s.jpg\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124056ODozTF7p23PRlH4V.gif\" title=\"啊\" alt=\"啊\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/david-brandon-geeting-4\" target=\"_blank\">itsnicethat</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}